[[Image:Urban street art at Sawtelle Boulevard, Los Angeles, California.jpg|thumb|250px|A variety of street posters on an abandoned billboard in [[Sawtelle, Los Angeles, California]].]] '''Street poster art''' is a kind of [[graffiti]], more specifically categorized as "street art". Posters are usually handmade or printed graphics on thin paper. It can be understood as an art piece that is installed on the streets as opposed to in a gallery or museum, but by some it is not comprehended as a form of [[contemporary art]].
